contentheadline.headline: Wikipedia:Votes for deletion/Paper Mache or Papier Maché

contentrichtext.text: The page name [[Paper Mache or Papier Maché]] is more than one expression. I have redirected it to [[Papier-mâché]], but the redirect still irks me a bit. The original content was also Copyvio. Delete? -- [[User:Chris 73|Chris 73]] | [[User talk:Chris 73|Talk]] 02:40, 6 May 2004 (UTC) * Delete. Existing names are sufficient. [[User:Topbanana|TB]] 08:22, 6 May 2004 (UTC) *Delete. --[[User:Brockert|Ben Brockert]] 01:52, May 9, 2004 (UTC) *Delete the redirect - who would ever look for anything that phrase? [[User:Pteron|Pteron]] 00:47, 11 May 2004 (UTC) *Delete the redirect [[User:Jfdwolff|JFW]] | [[User_talk:Jfdwolff|<small>T@lk</small>]] 10:14, 11 May 2004 (UTC) *Delete. --[[User:217.118.43.92|217.118.43.92]] 18:28, 11 May 2004 (UTC)
